(429, 8, 'career_main_new', 'a:1:{i:0;a:8:{s:5:"title";s:25:"NEW GRAD TRAINING PROGRAM";s:8:"subtitle";s:11:"Brazil Only";s:16:"background-image";s:3:"143";s:4:"text";s:1384:"<p>Avenue Code&rsquo;s <span class="text_orange">New Grad Training Program</span> is an exciting opportunity for newly graduated professionals to develop UI or QA expertise through hands-on work experience.<br />\r\nNew members of the Avenue Code family will partner with experienced developers who will guide them through a three month course in technology and best practices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trainees will gain experience in:</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="text_orange text_ident">- Devising and implementing internal projects of Avenue Code.<br />\r\n- Developing and delivering presentations about technology at our Bootcamp meetings.<br />\r\n- Building and refining prototypes using newly acquired skills and knowledges.<br />\r\n- Participating online in technology communities.<br />\r\n- Reading articles and researching technology sites for information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We currently have positions available in: <strong>QA and UI</strong><br />\r\nInterested? Send us your resume! Contact us at: <a href="mailto:jobs.brazil@avenuecode.com?subject=New Grad Program">jobs.brazil@avenuecode.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Program Requirements:</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="text_orange text_ident">- Knowledge of Agile Methodologies<br />\r\n- Passion for Testing or UI Development<br />\r\n- Proficiency in Computer Science, Information Systems, Software Engineering or related subjects.<br />\r\n- At most 6 months since date of graduation</p>\r\n";s:7:"image-1";s:3:"144";s:7:"image-2";s:3:"145";s:7:"image-3";s:3:"146";s:7:"image-4";s:3:"147";}}'),
