(285, 1, '2015-05-21 20:24:02', '2015-05-21 20:24:02', '<p class="releaseDateline" style="color: #000000;">San Francisco, CA (PRWEB) January 09, 2014</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">Avenue Code, an IT consulting firm specializing in <a style="color: #07689b;" title="Avenue Code" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL3d3dy5hdmVudWVjb2RlLmNvbQ==" rel="nofollow">agile software development methodologies</a>, announces that it recently opened its third office in Brazil—this time in São Paulo—in addition to two existing locations in Belo Horizonte.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">Avenue Code sees the expansion in Brazil as a timely strategic movement in light of the nation’s booming economy. With a planned expenditure of US $35 billion for three new soccer stadiums, Brazil expects to reap huge economical benefits from the 2014 World Cup. In addition, Brazil is to host the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, bringing the nation to the attention of investors and businesses worldwide.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">With its new offices located in Jardins, the prestigious business district in São Paulo, Avenue Code plans to cater to the tech-hungry organizations in the area. São Paulo, aka the “Concrete Jungle,” established its fame as the technology hub of South America, largely due to the presence of numerous international technology companies such as Airbnb, Google, and Walmart Brazil.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">Marking the company’s largest expansion, the São Paulo office strategically positions Avenue Code in the upcoming year for engagements with Latin American clients and North American clients based in Brazil. Avenue Code’s co-founder Zeo Solomon explains, “To date we have catered predominantly to clients in North America from our Brazilian development center in Belo Horizonte; but the São Paulo location will unlock new opportunities for Latin American clients, a region of increasing importance to the global economy.”</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">The newest executive to join Avenue Code, Alexandre Bioza, Head of Business and Consulting in Brazil, adds: “Since we opened in Brazil four years ago, our business has rapidly grown and we are now focused on expanding our client base in São Paulo, the largest business center of South America. We provide IT services for both near and on-shore clients and we are set to grow and aggressively compete with our innovative and agile business model.”</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">About Avenue Code:\r\nAvenue Code is a <a style="color: #07689b;" title="Avenue Code" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL3d3dy5hdmVudWVjb2RlLmNvbQ==" rel="nofollow">full-service information technology consulting</a> and development organization that specializes in Agile Methodologies. We have been serving dozens of fortune 100 eCommerce companies, with a breadth of experience in <a style="color: #07689b;" title="Service Offerings" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL2F2ZW51ZWNvZGUuY29tL3NlcnZpY2VzLmh0bWw=" rel="nofollow">eCommerce</a>, <a style="color: #07689b;" title="Omni-channel technology" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL2F2ZW51ZWNvZGUuY29tL2NvbnRlbnQvb21uaS1jaGFubmVs" rel="nofollow">omni-channel technology</a>, and <a style="color: #07689b;" title="Mobile Development" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL2F2ZW51ZWNvZGUuY29tL01vYmlsZV9EZXZlbG9wbWVudA==" rel="nofollow">mobile development</a>. Our solutions help our clients build sustainable success.</p>', 'San Francisco–based IT Consulting Company, Avenue Code, Makes a Strategic Expansion in Brazil by Opening Its Third Office', 'Avenue Code makes a strategic decision to expand its Brazil presence to São Paulo, its third office in Brazil following the earlier establishment of two offices in Belo Horizonte.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'san-francisco-based-it-consulting-company-avenue-code-makes-a-strategic-expansion-in-brazil-by-opening-its-third-office', '', '', '2015-05-21 20:24:02', '2015-05-21 20:24:02', '', 0, 'http://revamp.avenuecode.com/?post_type=release&#038;p=285', 0, 'release', '', 0),
(286, 1, '2015-05-21 20:24:26', '2015-05-21 20:24:26', '<p class="releaseDateline" style="color: #000000;">San Francisco, CA (PRWEB) February 13, 2014</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">Avenue Code, an <a style="color: #07689b;" title="Avenue Code" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL3d3dy5hdmVudWVjb2RlLmNvbQ==" rel="nofollow">IT management consulting firm in San Francisco</a>, has announced that it will be an official sponsor of DeveloperWeek SF 2014, a week-long conference and expo hosting thousands of developers who will build new applications, product features, and learn new skills within one week. DeveloperWeek focuses on helping developers, designers, and entrepreneurs build as many new apps in a month as possible.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">As an official sponsor, Avenue Code will be giving a forty-minute talk on how to build a multi-million-dollar e-business website in an hour, under the title, “Building Large eCommerce Sites” to be presented by Prashant Palsokar, Director of Technology, and Mike Rose, Managing Consultant.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">In addition, Avenue Code will be hosting a virtual Code Challenge, for which developers will write and submit code for the challenge to win a scholarship of up to $500. During their two-day exhibition, Avenue Code’s developers will be present to educate and answer any questions attendees may have. Also, they will be inviting attendees to their open house at their headquarters in San Francisco from 5pm to 8pm on February 18th. This will give people a chance to talk with the Senior Management and have a “behind the scenes” look at their office.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">With 250+ speakers, 2,500 attendees, and 400 Data &amp; API Technologies in one city, Avenue Code is proud to be a sponsor of DeveloperWeek.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">One of the founders of Avenue Code, Zeo Solomon remarks, “DeveloperWeek in San Francisco is a home away from home. We see our offices as an extension of the event and that\'s what we\'re planning to be. We invite all of you bright and like-minded techies to come say “hello,” and have a friendly drink.”</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">About Avenue Code:\r\nAvenue Code is a full-service information technology consulting and development organization that specializes in <a style="color: #07689b;" title="Avenue Code" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL3d3dy5hdmVudWVjb2RlLmNvbQ==" rel="nofollow">Agile Methodologies</a>. We have been serving dozens of Fortune 100 eCommerce companies, with a breadth of experience in eCommerce, omni-channel technology, and mobile development. Our solutions help our clients build sustainable success.</p>', 'Avenue Code Will Be an Official Sponsor of DeveloperWeek SF 2014', 'Avenue Code is sponsoring DeveloperWeek SF 2014, which celebrates the latest technology, learning, and developers.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'avenue-code-will-be-an-official-sponsor-of-developerweek-sf-2014', '', '', '2015-05-21 20:24:26', '2015-05-21 20:24:26', '', 0, 'http://revamp.avenuecode.com/?post_type=release&#038;p=286', 0, 'release', '', 0),
(287, 1, '2015-05-21 20:24:51', '2015-05-21 20:24:51', '<p class="releaseDateline" style="color: #000000;">San Francisco, CA (PRWEB) July 23, 2014</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">Avenue Code, a <a class="trackingLink" style="color: #07689b;" title="Avenue Code" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL3d3dy5hdmVudWVjb2RlLmNvbQ==" rel="nofollow">management consulting firm</a> specializing in Agile software development methodologies, today announced that it has achieved Gold Partner status in <a class="trackingLink" style="color: #07689b;" title="Oracle PartnerNetwork" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL3d3dy5vcmFjbGUuY29tL3VzL3BhcnRuZXJzaGlwcy9pbmRleC5odG0=" rel="nofollow">Oracle PartnerNetwork</a> (OPN). By attaining Gold Level membership, Oracle has recognized Avenue Code for its commitment to establish Oracle related knowledge in delivering eCommerce implementations for its clients, including Fortune 100 companies and for uniquely addressing the challenges of joint customers and large IT organizations going through Agile transformation and Agile software development.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">With Oracle Gold Level membership, Avenue Code will continue to expand their four main service offerings—IT management consulting, Project Ownership and Implementation, Engineering and Agile Professionals, and the Avenue Code Academy. Avenue Code provides high quality consultants that are equipped with knowledge about Oracle Cloud, Java, MySQL, and other Oracle products. Avenue Code also provides Avenue Code Academy training services with Oracle-related products.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">Amir Razmara, managing partner of Avenue Code, said, “We are a strategic partner to several Fortune 100 retail companies. We provide them with high-level ATG consultants, as well as Java and Agile-trained managing consultants. Our consultants have all experienced significant value from Oracle’s Gold Level membership benefits.”</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">With its Gold status, Avenue Code receives the benefit of being able to start developing specializations that will allow them to grow their business, increase their expertise, reach higher levels of customer retention, and create differentiation in the marketplace. Gold members also become eligible to resell all Oracle Technology products and can apply to resell Oracle Applications and Industry Solutions. In addition, they receive access to Oracle account representatives and My Oracle Support updates for all products, discounts on training, limited free assessment/exam vouchers, reduced rates on the purchase of Oracle licenses for internal use, discounts on advances customer services and more. For more information about the benefits of becoming an OPN Gold level partner, please visit: <a class="trackingLink" style="color: #07689b;" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL3d3dy5vcmFjbGUuY29tL3VzL3BhcnRuZXJzaGlwcy9pbmRleC5odG0=" rel="nofollow">http://www.oracle.com/us/partnerships/index.htm</a></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">About Avenue Code Avenue Code is a full-service information technology consulting and development organization that specializes in<a class="trackingLink" style="color: #07689b;" title="Avenue Code" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL3d3dy5hdmVudWVjb2RlLmNvbQ==" rel="nofollow">Agile Methodologies</a>. We have been serving dozens of Fortune 100 eCommerce companies, with a breadth of experience in eCommerce, omni-channel technology, and mobile development. Our solutions help our clients build sustainable success.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">About Oracle PartnerNetwork Oracle PartnerNetwork (OPN) Specialized is the latest version of Oracle\'s partner program that provides partners with tools to better develop, sell and implement Oracle solutions. OPN Specialized offers resources to train and support specialized knowledge of Oracle products and solutions and has evolved to recognize Oracle\'s growing product portfolio, partner base and business opportunity. Key to the latest enhancements to OPN is the ability for partners to differentiate through Specializations. Specializations are achieved through competency development, business results, expertise and proven success. To find out more visit <a class="trackingLink" style="color: #07689b;" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL3d3dy5vcmFjbGUuY29tL3BhcnRuZXJz" rel="nofollow">http://www.oracle.com/partners</a>.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">###</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">Trademarks Oracle and Java are registered trademarks of Oracle and/or its affiliates.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;"></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;"><a href="http://avenuecode.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/oracle_300x400.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-661" src="http://avenuecode.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/oracle_300x400.jpg" alt="Oracle PartnerNetwork" width="400" height="300" /></a></p>', 'Avenue Code Becomes Oracle PartnerNetwork Gold Level Partner', 'Avenue Code, a management consulting firm specializing in Agile software development methodologies, today announced that it has achieved Gold Partner status in Oracle PartnerNetwork (OPN).', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'avenue-code-becomes-oracle-partnernetwork-gold-level-partner', '', '', '2015-05-21 20:24:51', '2015-05-21 20:24:51', '', 0, 'http://revamp.avenuecode.com/?post_type=release&#038;p=287', 0, 'release', '', 0),
(288, 1, '2015-05-21 20:25:12', '2015-05-21 20:25:12', '<p class="releaseDateline" style="color: #000000;">San Francisco, California (PRWEB) August 27, 2014</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">For a limited time, San Francisco-based consulting firm Avenue Code is offering <a style="color: #07689b;" title="2-DAY CERTIFIED SCRUM MASTER TRAINING" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL2F2ZW51ZWNvZGUuY29tL3Byb2R1Y3QvMi1kYXktY2VydGlmaWVkLXNjcnVtLW1hc3Rlci10cmFpbmluZy8=" rel="nofollow">Certified Scrum Master Training classes</a> taught by an internationally Certified Scrum Trainer (CST), Robyn Dymond, for their clients and the general public.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">The first of these two-day courses will take place October 4th-5th at Avenue Code’s office in the Financial District. The course will teach participants the Scrum and Agile principles through exercises and case studies designed to familiarize students with Agile and Scrum and help them develop proficiency in applying these principles in their day-to-day practices.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">“Agile software development is cutting-edge expertise in modern software development. Our clients have benefited for years by using Avenue Code to implement large scale eCommerce solutions using this methodology. We are very excited to bring our deep knowledge of Agile to a larger audience through Avenue Code\'s public Agile classes,” the managing partner, Amir Razmara said.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">Avenue Code consults with Fortune 500 ecommerce companies in the Bay Area. They help their clients apply fundamental Agile practices to the implementation of their technical solutions, and in doing so, increase their ROI and stay updated with rapidly changing consumer demands. Agile fundamentals—team empowerment, frequent delivery of products, and testing early and often throughout the project lifecycle—can be implemented in the IT side of many industries.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">The Scrum Master training program is one of the classes being offered as part of Avenue Code Academy, which represents an additional offering for Avenue Code’s customers. Avenue Code also provides expertise in <a style="color: #07689b;" title="Avenue Code Services" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL2F2ZW51ZWNvZGUuY29tL3NlcnZpY2VzLw==" rel="nofollow">management consulting, project ownership and implementation, and skilled engineering professionals</a>.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">This training program is unique in that participants will be able to segue into an ongoing relationship with Avenue Code. Participants will not only build hands-on proficiency, but will also have access to further coaching and consultation from Avenue Code representatives. Moreover, participants will receive a two-year membership in the Scrum Alliance and an online knowledge assessment by Scrum Alliance for certification upon completion of the course.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">About Avenue Code:\r\nAvenue Code is a full-service information technology consulting and development organization that specializes in<a style="color: #07689b;" title="Avenue Code" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL2F2ZW51ZWNvZGUuY29tLw==" rel="nofollow">Agile Methodologies</a>. We have been serving dozens of Fortune 100 e-commerce companies, with a breadth of experience in e-commerce, omni-channel technology, and mobile development. Our solutions help our clients build sustainable success.</p>', 'San Francisco Consulting Firm Offers Certified Scrum Training Program to the Public', 'Beginning in October, San Francisco-based consulting firm, Avenue Code, will be offering Certified Scrum Master Training classes to the public. The company, which consults for top e-commerce companies in the Bay Area, is adding this new service line to expand implementation of Agile principles throughout the industry.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'san-francisco-consulting-firm-offers-certified-scrum-training-program-to-the-public', '', '', '2015-05-21 20:25:12', '2015-05-21 20:25:12', '', 0, 'http://revamp.avenuecode.com/?post_type=release&#038;p=288', 0, 'release', '', 0) ;
